text: Google Currents, or Google Current, may refer to: * Google Currents, an app developed by Google for internal enterprise communication, still in development with beta version released in 2019 * Google Currents (2011–13), an app developed by Google that provided electronic access to full-length magazine articles from 2011 to 2013 * Google Current, a five-minute-long television program that aired every half hour on Current TV from 2005 to 2007 Category:Google
title: Google Currents (disambiguation)
